\id HAB  
\h Habakkuk 
\toc1 Habakkuk Themgao Lekhabu 
\toc2 Habakkuk 
\toc3 Habakkuk 
\mt1 HABAKKUK  
\mt2 THEMGAO LEKHABU  
\mt3 Habakkuk Themgao Lekhabu Sung Thu  
\ip Habakkuk hin Pathen thudoh hahsa tah chu ana dongin, hichu themgao lekhabu dang tobang loubeh hiche lekhabu hi ahin sundoh theijin ahi. Chule Habakkuk hin Pathen adohna le Pathen'in Habakkuk adonbutna ho hi themgaopa hin ana jih ahi.  
\ip Habakkuk in thumvei Pathen kom’a thu anasei in, hiche lekhabu hi hop thum’a hopkhen thei asodoh in ahi. Amasa bung-2 sunga hin themgao Habakkuk in Pathen thudoh nivei abol’in chule ajona pen in, bung-3 sunga Pathen thangvahna taona thudol ajihlut in ahi. Aman, Pathen'in amite chonsetna avetthim hi oimona aneiyin, hinlah Pathen'in amite chonsetna jeh chun, Babylonte hunguva Jerusalem soh’a ahung puimang diu thudol aseipeh in ahi.  
\ip Hinlah amite sanga chonse khohse cheh Babylonte chu iti dana gimbolna beija akoi ding ham, ti thudol adohnaa chun—Babylonte chu gimbolna thoh louva akoilou ding thua, athudoh chu donbutna aneiyin ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Ajih Kum  
\ip Hiche lekhabu hi Habakkuk themgao in Judah namsung Pathen’a kon agamlat pettah-u, chule Babylon ten Jerusalem ahung lah masang jep-uva anajih ahi. Hichu 610-605 BC vel-a anajih ahi.  
\is1 Hiche Phat Laiya Thilsoh Umdol  
\ip Hiche phatlai hin, Judah phung sunga chonset ana hoise lheh in, milim houna’a achateu maicham thilto in ana tohdoh jiuvin ahi. Pathen hing leh dihtah chu ana hepha tapouve! Judah te lengpa gilou tah Jehoiakim chun Pathen themgao ho thusei angailou goh hilouvin, aman themgao ho lekhajih jong meiyin ahal in, chule atha jong ana um'in ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Themgao Thudohna  
\p
\v 1 Hiche hi Habakkuk themgaovin thilmu aneina thudol ahi.  
\v 2 Vo PAKAI, itihchan geija panpi ngaichaa kakou kou di hitam? Hinla nangin nei ngaipeh poi! “Muntin'a nosopma kibolna aumtai!” Ka kap in, hinla eipanhu dingin na hungpoi.  
\v 3 Hiche gitlou kibol ho hi kavet vet jing ding hitam? Hiche gim gentheina ho jouse hi ibol’a kavet vet jeng ding ham? Keiman kavet chanin mahthahna le nosopma kibolna hobou ka mudoh’e. Mi nelkal hat ho leh kinahpia hat mihonpi chun eihin umkimvel tauve.  
\v 4 Dan hi donlou tobangbep chu ahitai, chule thutanna munho’a jong thudih umtalou ahi. Migilou ho chun midih ho sanga gamchenga atamjoh jeh uvin, thudih chu heikoija um bepma ahitai.   
\s1 Pakai akon donbutna  
\p
\v 5 Pakai chun adonbut in, “Chitin namtin ho khu gahven chuleh kidangsa temin! Ajeh chu keiman nangma nikho laiya hi thil khat kahin boldoh ding, mi koiham khat touvin seijongleh na tahsan louhel ding chu kahinbol ding ahije. \x + \xo 1:5 \xt Act 13:41\x*  
\v 6 Keiman Babylon mite ho, giloutah le nosopma mibol ho chu ka hin tundoh ding ahi. Ama hon vannoi muntin apaltan’uva kijotle ding’u chule gam dang tampi ahinjo dingu ahi. \x + \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Lengte 24:2\x*  
\v 7 Amaho hi gitlou abol nauva engsetah’a chonna ahiuvin, chutia abolnom chengseu chu abol’u ahi.  
\v 8 Sakol aneihou jong lutnu sangin alhai hatjouvin, khomu chipchep a ngeihon lhakhom sangin jong ahoise jouve. Sakol kangtalaija touho chun gamla tah a kon'in a sakol ho’u chu ahin thunun jeng uvin; Muvanlai lengle hon a anchah’u abokhumuva avallhum jiu kisei tobang ahiuve.  
\v 9 Oh, ahung tauve, abonchauvin nosopma boldin akunsuh tauve. A gancha hon hou jong chu nelphaija hui bangin ahung kitol’un, amasanguva asohchang ho’u ahin masot hou chu neldi tamin atam jeng uvin ahi .  
\v 10 ama hon leng ho le leng chapa te ho chu isahlou tah in abolun, chule akulpi ho jouse chu isah loutah in abol uve.  
\v 11 Amaho chu hui nung bangin akitolun chule achemang tauve. Hinla amaho sungil’a themmona nei ahiuve, athahat uchu pathena nei ahiuve.”  
\v 12 Vo Pakai ka Pathen, nangma tonsotna um, ka Mithengpa Nangman nei theh manghel jeng hih nauvin nate na? Vo Pakai, ka Songpiu, nangman hiche Babylon mite hi eisudih dinguleh ka chonsetna ho’u atam jeh a ei-gimbol ding uva na hinsol ahi.  
\v 13 Nangma hila athenga nahin chule agilou chu n maikoh a um theilou ahi. Chuti ahileh amaho do’ha joulhepna namitsat ding hijaham? Mi engsete chun asanguva chonphajo avallhumu jongleh thipbeh a naum ding hitam?  
\v 14 Keiho hi ahinga kimandoh dinga le akithat dinga kiman ho tobangbep kahiuvem? Kei ho hi twikhanglen na um ganhing ho lamkai bei tobangbep ka hiuvem?  
\v 15 Amaho kipanaa le golnop bolna ding uva, ngakoija eiki khaidoh dinga chuleh lensunga ohden bep ding bou kahi dingu hitam?  
\v 16 Chutengleh ama hon lenthang anei hou chu Pathen tobangin houvun tin, chuleh amasanguva chun gimnamtui halna nei uvinte. Amaho chun, “Hiche lenthang pathen ho hin keiho eihaodoh sah’u ahi” ati ding’u ahi.  
\v 17 Nangman amaho hi hiti dinmun'a hi nasolmangpai pai ding ham? Amaho hi phottohna beihella agaljouva hi i-tiha maipah jing dingu hitam?   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Kagalvenna mun'a chun kaldoh ingting chuleh ka pansatna mun'a chun dinging’e. Chu che mun'a konna chu Pakaiyin kajaha ipi aseiding ve’ing ting chuleh keima kiphinna iti eidonbut nem ti ngah-inge.   
\s1 Midih Ho Ki Hinso Ding  
\p
\v 2 Chutah in Pakaiyin kajah a, “Ka donbutna hi songpheng ho chunga jihdoh in, hiti henlang hileh, alhaile pa chun midang ho kom'a thu phatea agalhut thei ding ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche ahunglhung ding kimu hi khonung’a ding ahi. Hiche hin achaina ding ahilchenin, chule hiche hin gu ilhungtei ding ahi. Ahung vaigeija ahijongleh, ngah hat in, ajeh chu kho ngaisot louding, hunglhung tei ding ahi. \x + \xo 2:3 \xt Heb 10:37\x*  
\v 4 Mi kilesah chu vetem in! Amaho tah akisong uvin, chuleh ahinkho mandan’u chu akon chetchut nin ahi. Hinlah midih chu Pathen a dinga tahsan aum nauva hing ding ahiuve. \x + \xo 2:4 \xt Rm 1:17; Gal 3:11; Heb 10:38\x*   
\s1 Mi giloute Pohgih  
\p
\v 5 Nei le nga hao mana lungngahna thei ahidehpoi, chuleh mihoitho hon kicholdona anei hih uve. Ama hon lhan tobangin akamu chu ahonglenun, chuleh thina kisei tobangin aphatai atipouve. Akiloset manuvin ama hon namtina mi akhom khomuvin, chuleh mitampi chu aval lhum tauve.  
\v 6 Hinla asoh chan loi jengu hin amaho ajumso ding’u ahi. Amaho chun dai thanopna anei uva, Migucha nangho itobang lunghemna in nahin phah diu hitam? Tua hi nachan ding dol’u na kimu ding’u ahi! Alam louva na hung hao dohu ahin, hinlah itih chanpi hi hitia na masot nahlai dingu ham?  
\v 7 Phulouhel ouva na leibatna houvin nachung uva thutanna nanei khum ding’u ahi. Na chunguva hungkiheijuva kicha le tija'a nadinpet’uva nanei jouseu nalahpeh dingu ahi.  
\v 8 Ajeh chu nang hon namtin vaipi nei jouse nachom jeng’u ahin, tua hi ason achilhah ho jouseu chun nangho nei achom dingu ahi. Nanghon thinglhang gam pumpia tolthana nabol uvin chuleh khopi ho chu alam louva gimbolna in na lodimsah tauve.  
\v 9 Alam louva phatchomna naholnauva konna in lentah tah nasahu hin itobang lunggim nan nahin lhunkhum ding’u hitam! Nagou haonauvin huhbit nachoh pehthei dingin na tahsan’un, hahsatna in aphah joulouna ding mun'a na insung mi busatsah a nahiuve.  
\v 10 Hinlah tolthana nabol jeh a hi, namin na jachat sah a chuleh nahinkhou nachan lo-u ahitai.  
\v 11 Banga song ho hin nangho douna a kholhang ahinsap doh ding, chule inchunga inkam kilhunna inching noilama kidap hon jong noplouna ahin phondoh ding ahi.  
\v 12 Tolthana le a lamlouva sumtong mu’a konna khopi sadoh ho itobang lunghem nan na hinphah diu hitam!  
\v 13 Van Sepai ho Pakai chun namtin vaipi ahaonau hi vutvai kisopeh ding ahi tia ana thutepsa hilou ham? Na tampi atohdohu jong aboncha panna bei ahi.  
\v 14 Tihon twikhanglen in achup bangin, leiset hi Pakai loupina hetna in alodim ding ahi. \x + \xo 2:14 \xt Isa 11:9\x*  
\v 15 Naheng nakom kham ngolsah a nangma itobang lungkhamnan nahin phah ding hitam! Nakhon chu achung uva na ngamin, amaho chu adasa sauvin a jachatpiu sagohkeu ahinau chu deitah a navet theina dingin nabollin ahi.  
\v 16 Hinla kintah a na chunga minset sahna hunglhung ding ahi. Hungin, donin chuleh muthei din kilangdohin. Pakai thutanna khon’a kon chun hung donin, chule na loupinau jouse chu jachatna hin sodoh hen.  
\v 17 Nanghon Lebanon gammang ho chu na satchaijui. Tua hi nangho kisatlha ding nahiuve. Nanghon gamsa ho chu na sumang hel’ui, hijeha hi amaho kicha a na um’u ahitai. Agamsung pumpia toltha nabol uvin, chule khopi ho jong chu nosopa kibolna nadip dimu ahitai.  
\v 18 Mihem khutnin asem milim chu ipi phatchomna uma ahilouleh nalhemlhauva pang milim kilhajol chu phamonga hinam? Nakhut tahun asem thil tahsan chu ipi phatchomna ham, pathen kihoulimpi thei hilou chu!  
\v 19 Thinga konna kisem milimho jaha, “Khangin lang chule nei huhdoh un” tiho chunga itobang lunghemna in nanga’u hitam! Thusei theilou song milim kisem ho jah a, “Thoudoh un chuleh neihilun” natiuve. Milim khat nin ipi bol ding nahil theijum? Sana le dangka a kisem himaithei junte, hinla ama hon asung uva hinna anei pouve.  
\v 20 Hinlah Pakai hi Ahou In Thenga aum’e. Leiset pumpi a angsunga thipchet hen”.   
\c 3  
\s1 Themgaopa Taona  
\p
\v 1 Hiche taona hi themgao Habakkuk in lakaija ahin sahdoh ahi.  
\v 2 Pakai, nangma chung chang thu hi abkonna kana jahsa ahi. Na thilbol ho hi kadatmo lheh jengin ahi. Achesa kum ho’a nana bolsa ahi bangin, ka ngaichat dehset petlaitahu hin nei panpi kituvin. Chuleh na lunghan laitah a jong mikhoto them nahina chu geldoh in.  
\v 3 Keiman Pathen chun Edom gal lama patna gamthip ahinjot galkai kamu’n, Paran molchunga konna Mitheng Pa chu ahung kamui. Avah emsengsung chun vanthamjol alodimin, chuleh leiset chung hi avahchoinan alodim jengin ahi.  
\v 4 Ahungna chu nisa hung sohdoh bangin akilang jenge. Akhutna kon'in vah ahung kikhodohin, athaneina kiselna mun'a konna hungdoh a ahi.  
\v 5 Amasanga amangthah ding ho akijotnun, chule anunglama pulin ahinjuipaijin ahi.  
\v 6 Ama adinleh leiset akithingin, avetna ahileh namtin vaipi akihot jenguve. Tonsotna ana um mol ho chu athechehin, chuleh a i-tiha thinglhang anaum ho chu asuchamin ahi. Ama Tonsotna Umpa chu ahi.  
\v 7 Keiman Kushan miho chu lunglhatah a a’umu kamun, chule Median namte jong chu kicha a tijatah a a’umu kamui.  
\v 8 Pakai, nangman lunghanga twi chu najepma, twipi chu kikhena hija ham? Amaho chunga lunghimoa nahim? Ahipoi, nangin huhhingna sakol kangtalai chu nahin sol ahijo me!  
\v 9 Nangin nathal le na thalchang koina na livathei chu napeije. Nangman leiset hi vadung twi ho lonna dingin na hongdohin ahi.  
\v 10 Mol ho akivetle akithingin, twi kinong chun amasanglama ahin nuhin ahi. Twi thuh tah chun ahin samdohin, akhut chun Pakai lam ahin sang’e.  
\v 11 Nisa le lha chu nathalchang ho jangkeija alenna chule natengcha vallihleh chu akipeipet in vanlaijolla ading dentai.  
\v 12 Nangman gamsung chu lunghangin napaltanin, chule chitin namtin chu lunghangin nachotpha tai.  
\v 13 Na lhenchomte huhdoh dingin, nathaonute huhdohna dingin nakipat dohtai. Nangin migilou luchang chu na noigepin chule alua pat akengtou geijin najep pehtai.  
\v 14 Huipi hungnung banga hung kitola, bailamtah a Israel bahgam dinga go chu, nangin ama galvon maman nasumang’e.  
\v 15 Nangman twipi chu nasakolla na paljengin, chule twi thahat tah chu sangtah in kiting denin na umsah jeng’e.  
\v 16 Hiche thu kajah in kasungil akithing jengin, ka muh jong kichatnan aphusepsupmin, kakengteni jong akihot hotnin, chule kichat tijatnan kakithing jenge. Keiman ka chunguva gal hungbol mipi ho chu vangsetna nasatah in ahinphah dingu nikho chu thipkhencha kanga ahitai.   
\s1 Tahsanna Zaila  
\p
\v 17 Theichang phungho jong chu pahdoh hih uhenlang, lengpi guija lengpiga ho umhih hen; Olive phunga thao putdoh tahih jong  
\p leh, chuleh loujao hoa ima pou hih henlang chuleh ga sodoh tahih jong uleh; chuleh loujao hoa gancha ho thi’u henlang, ganhing ho jeng jong chu agoh in umu henlang hita jongleh;   
\p
\v 18 Keima Pakai a kipah nalai ding kahi! Ei huhhingpa Pathenna chu kipahna lai ding kahi!  
\v 19 Leng vaipo thaneipen Pakai chu ka thahatna ahi! Sa san bangin keng thaneina pen tin, munsang lai laiya jong eichopsah ding ahi. (Zai pipu chun: Hiche taona hi semjang khao tampi tothoa atumginga alamkai ding ahi.) \x + \xo 3:19 \xt 2 Samuel 22:34; Labu 18:33\x*   